quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  92,1,Paliusikupamenemdimaumayamba
  92,2,Ndimasanapamene kumayera
  92,3,Ndi pali Iye amene adalenga chachimuna ndi chachikazi
  92,4,Ndithudi zochita zanu zonse zili ndi mapeto osiyana
  92,5,Akakhala iye amene amapereka chaulere ndipo amamuopa Mulungu
  92,6,Ndipo amakhulupirira pochita zinthu zabwino
  92,7,Ife tidzamusalazira njira yake ya ku chipulumutso
  92,8,Koma iye amene sapereka chaulere ndipo amaganiza kuti ndi woima payekha
  92,9,Sakhulupirira ndipo sachita ntchito zabwino
  92,10,Tidzamusalazira njira yake ya ku chionongeko
  92,11,Kodi chuma chake chidzamuthandiza chiani pamene iye azidzazunzika
  92,12,Ndithudi ndi udindo wathu kupereka chilangizo
  92,13,"Ndipo, ndithudi, zonse za m’moyo umene uli nkudza ndi za m’moyo uno ndi zathu"
  92,14,Motero ndakuchenjezani za moto wa lawilawi
  92,15,"Kulibe Al-Dhuha\t655 munthu amene akapsye nawo kupatula munthu wochita zoipa"
  92,16,Amene amakana choonadi ndipo safuna kumvera chenjezo
  92,17,"Koma anthu onse olungama, adzatalikirana nawo"
  92,18,Amene amapereka chaulere chake poonjezera kudziyeretsa
  92,19,Osati chifukwa chakuti afuna kupezako cholowa ayi
  92,20,"Kupatula ndi cholinga chopeza chisomo cha Ambuye wake, wapamwamba mwamba"
  92,21,Ndithudi iye adzasangalala